Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:06.07,japanese,,0,0,0,,死ぬ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.07,0:00:09.90,japanese,,0,0,0,,自然と一体になることが\Nどうして死ぬことなんだってばよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:13.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,ガマ吉 死ねとはなんじゃ 死ねとは。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.40,0:00:15.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,変な例えを出すな！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.33,0:00:17.90,japanese,,0,0,0,,だって…。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.90,0:00:22.77,japanese,,0,0,0,,安心せえ 実際に ナルトちゃんが\N死ぬわけじゃありゃへん。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.77,0:00:24.77,japanese,,0,0,0,,なら いったい？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.77,0:00:27.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,ワシの話を最後まで聞け。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.40,0:00:30.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,順を追って 話すけんのう。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.27,0:00:36.07,japanese,,0,0,0,,(フカサク)自然エネルギーを\N己に取り込むというのは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.07,0:00:39.90,japanese,,0,0,0,,それを感じとり\N己に吸い寄せることが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:41.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,できるようになる\Nということじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:45.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,更に 自然と一体になることで➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.40,0:00:48.23,japanese,,0,0,0,,自然エネルギーの身体への出入りを➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:52.57,japanese,,0,0,0,,自由に\Nコントロールできるようにもなる。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.57,0:00:56.73,japanese,,0,0,0,,修業の内容を\N具体的に言うとじゃな。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.73,0:00:58.67,japanese,,0,0,0,,うん うん！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.67,0:01:00.70,japanese,,0,0,0,,動くな。\Nは？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.70,0:01:03.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,動かんということじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:07.17,japanese,,0,0,0,,自然エネルギーは\N動物としての流れを止め➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.17,0:01:09.83,japanese,,0,0,0,,自然の流れと調和したときに➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.83,0:01:12.73,japanese,,0,0,0,,初めて感じとることができる。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.73,0:01:15.70,japanese,,0,0,0,,つまり 動かなきゃいいのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:18.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,なんか簡単そうだな それ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.50,0:01:22.49,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルト お前 わかっとらんのう。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.67,0:01:29.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,動物にとって 動かずにいることが\Nいちばんつらいんじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.50,0:01:34.17,japanese,,0,0,0,,跳んだり走ったり\N力入れてチャクラ練ったり➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.17,0:01:36.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,そんな修業ならやったけど➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.50,0:01:40.83,japanese,,0,0,0,,動くなって\Nいまいち ピンとこない修業だな。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:44.70,japanese,,0,0,0,,でも それで 自然エネルギーってのが\N取り込めるんだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:50.17,japanese,,0,0,0,,いきなりは ムリじゃ。\N時間がかかる修業じゃけんのう。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.17,0:01:53.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,これは かなり難度高めじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.20,0:01:55.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,そんなに時間がかかんのかよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.33,0:01:57.83,japanese,,0,0,0,,甘ったれるな ナルトちゃん。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.83,0:02:02.43,japanese,,0,0,0,,敵は輪廻眼\N六道仙人の力を持つ ペイン。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.43,0:02:05.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,自来也ちゃんを倒した強敵じゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:09.77,japanese,,0,0,0,,そんな心構えじゃ\N勝てりゃせんぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:12.60,japanese,,0,0,0,,そんなことは わかってる！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.60,0:02:15.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,ペインは 尾獣を狙う暁のリーダー。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.27,0:02:17.60,japanese,,0,0,0,,すぐにでも\Nオレのところへやってくる。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:20.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,あまり時間をかけてらんねえんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.93,0:02:25.97,japanese,,0,0,0,,まあ とはいっても➡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.97,0:02:29.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,もっと いい方法が\Nないこともないがのう。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.27,0:02:33.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,あんのかよ。\Nなら それで教えてくれよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:36.60,japanese,,0,0,0,,この後ろの滝。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:39.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,妙木山秘伝のガマ油じゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:41.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,ガマ油？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.77,0:02:46.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,ちょっと こっちへ来て\N片手出してみ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:48.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:57.77,japanese,,0,0,0,,ほい。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.77,0:03:03.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,このガマ油は\N自然エネルギーを引き寄せる力がある。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:05.87,japanese,,0,0,0,,修業の手助けをするものじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:08.53,japanese,,0,0,0,,アハハ 便利なのあんじゃん。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.53,0:03:11.87,japanese,,0,0,0,,この油を体に塗りつければ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:16.36,japanese,,0,0,0,,そこから自然エネルギーが\N体に入ってくるんじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:18.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,そうすれば だんだんと➡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:21.87,japanese,,0,0,0,,自然エネルギーを\N肌で感じるようになる。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.87,0:03:25.73,japanese,,0,0,0,,確かに\Nなんか 肌で感じる気がする。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.73,0:03:30.36,japanese,,0,0,0,,これは 感覚をつかむきっかけを\Nつくるものじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.36,0:03:34.87,japanese,,0,0,0,,いずれは 油がなくても\Nできるようになってくるが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.87,0:03:37.53,japanese,,0,0,0,,ただし リスクもある。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:40.43,japanese,,0,0,0,,えっ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:45.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,自然エネルギーコントロールが\N未熟な者に使うと➡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:49.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,カエルになっていくんじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:51.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,いぃ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:56.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,えぇ～!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:58.70,japanese,,0,0,0,,な な なんだ これ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:04:04.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,ああ 助けて！\Nカエルやだ！ ぎゃあ～!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.46,0:04:08.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,イッテ… 何すんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.13,0:04:10.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,戻った。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:12.97,japanese,,0,0,0,,(フカサク)すべては バランスじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:18.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,精神エネルギーと身体エネルギーは\N忍術チャクラで練り慣れとるから➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:21.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,バランスは取れるだろうがのう。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:24.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,そこに 外からの自然エネルギーも➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:27.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,バランスよく練りこむのは\N至難の業じゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:29.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,バランスか。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.63,0:04:33.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,少なすぎれば\N仙術チャクラはできん。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:37.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,かといって 多すぎれば\N自然エネルギーに取り込まれて➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:40.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,カエルになってしまう。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:46.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,多少 取り込みすぎたくらいなら\N元に戻すこともできるがのう。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:50.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,自然エネルギーを\N大幅に取り込みすぎたら➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:56.00,japanese,,0,0,0,,カエルになったまま\N二度と 元には戻れんようになる。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.00,0:04:58.00,japanese,,0,0,0,,さっき 死ぬっつったのは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:05:01.07,japanese,,0,0,0,,人として死ぬかもしれん\Nつうことじゃい。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:03.00,japanese,,0,0,0,,カエルになった者は➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:06.23,japanese,,0,0,0,,更に自然の一部に\Nなってしまうのじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.23,0:05:10.73,japanese,,0,0,0,,かつて 修業に失敗した者たちの\Nなれの果てが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:15.07,japanese,,0,0,0,,この石像たちじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.07,0:05:18.57,japanese,,0,0,0,,これ 全部…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:22.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,まあ 少しは安心せい。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:24.43,japanese,,0,0,0,,わしがついとるし➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.43,0:05:28.90,japanese,,0,0,0,,このハタキ棒は 自然エネルギーを\N外へ叩き出すものじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:32.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルトちゃんが\Nカエルに変化していくようなら➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:37.90,japanese,,0,0,0,,わしが これで\N逐一 叩き直してやるけんのう。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:40.23,japanese,,0,0,0,,はっきり言うとじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:44.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,あの自来也ちゃんですら\N完璧には こなせんかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:48.57,japanese,,0,0,0,,自来也ちゃんは\N仙術チャクラを練ると➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:51.60,japanese,,0,0,0,,少しカエルに化けてしもうとった。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:54.36,japanese,,0,0,0,,それでも\Nうまく練り込めたほうじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:57.90,japanese,,0,0,0,,ここまできて\N臆することもなかろうが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:00.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,一応 聞いておく。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:05.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,どうする？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:07.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,やる。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:12.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレの忍道は エロ仙人と同じだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:49.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,(マダラ)やっと六尾も揃ったか。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:52.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ペイン)これで すぐにでも\N九尾を狩りにいける。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:55.70,japanese,,0,0,0,,(マダラ)それがいい。\N自来也をやったことで➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:59.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,木ノ葉は\Nお前に目をつけたはずだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.46,0:08:01.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,時間が経てば経つほど➡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:04.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,向こうも\N何かしらの手を考えてくる。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:07.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,やりにくくなる前に動け。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:11.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,(小南)ペインは無敵…。\Nどんなことがあっても➡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:14.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,九尾は確実に手に入れる。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:16.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,尾獣は あと一匹。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:18.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,あと二匹では？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.30,0:08:20.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,すでに 八尾は\Nサスケが狩った。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:23.83,japanese,,0,0,0,,なるほど。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:27.73,japanese,,0,0,0,,小南 すぐに準備しろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:37.36,japanese,,0,0,0,,これから 木ノ葉へ向かう。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:48.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,イテッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.30,0:08:51.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,明日は 体中\N超内出血だってばよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:55.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,なんじゃ もうギブアップかいな。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:59.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,あのさ もっと要領のいい\N修業法があるんだってばよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.63,0:09:03.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,なんじゃそりゃ？\N影分身を使った修業法だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:07.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,そうすりゃ 経験値が\N何倍にもなるんだから。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.13,0:09:09.06,japanese,,0,0,0,,なるほどの。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:13.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,影分身の感覚は\Nオリジナルに還元されるからのう。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:17.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,しかしじゃ 逆に言うなら➡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.13,0:09:20.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,影分身が\N完全にカエルになってしもうたら➡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.46,0:09:22.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,オリジナルのほうも終わりじゃぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:26.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,んなことは わかってるよ！\Nよかろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:30.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,４人までじゃ。 それ以上は\Nわしのハタキ棒が間に合わん！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:33.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,よっしゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:38.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,イテッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:41.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,イタッ！\Nイテッ！\Nイタッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:43.00,japanese,,0,0,0,,おっ！\Nイテッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:45.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,もぐらたたきゲーム\Nやっとるんじゃねえんじゃぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:49.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,修業じゃ！\Nこれじゃ わしがもたん。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:51.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,クソッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.10,0:09:53.73,japanese,,0,0,0,,イテッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:57.60,japanese,,0,0,0,,これは 叩かれて\Nこんな顔になったんだってばよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:09:59.90,japanese,,0,0,0,,カエルになったんじゃねえって！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.90,0:10:01.89,japanese,,0,0,0,,なんじゃと… すまん。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:09.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,自然エネルギーを感じるだけの修業が➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:11.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,こんなに難しいとは思わなかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:16.56,japanese,,0,0,0,,つらい修業に耐えてこそ\N本当の力が手に入るのじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.56,0:10:18.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,それは わかってるよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:23.43,japanese,,0,0,0,,エロ仙人みてぇに強くなれんなら\N誰だって我慢するってもんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:26.73,japanese,,0,0,0,,いや それはムリじゃ。\Nえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:30.60,japanese,,0,0,0,,この修業は 誰もが\Nできるというわけではない。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:34.23,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルトちゃんと\N自来也ちゃんだからこそのもの。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:36.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,そう言っても ええ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:39.56,japanese,,0,0,0,,じゃなきゃ ここへは連れてこん。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.56,0:10:41.90,japanese,,0,0,0,,どういうことだってばよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:46.23,japanese,,0,0,0,,己の内に膨大なチャクラを持つ者。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:51.06,japanese,,0,0,0,,でなけりゃ たちまち自然エネルギーに\N取り込まれてしまうけんの。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:55.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,それだけ\N自然エネルギーはすごいのじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.33,0:10:57.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,はあ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:11:01.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,その上\Nあきらめん ド根性のある者。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:05.19,japanese,,0,0,0,,それが 仙人になれる人間じゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:09.83,japanese,,0,0,0,,よっしゃ！ やったるで！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:11.83,japanese,,0,0,0,,アホ!! 死ぬ気か！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:40.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,見えた！ やった！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:42.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,《どうやら\N少しは 自然エネルギーを➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:45.66,japanese,,0,0,0,,感じ取れるように\Nなってきたようじゃな》
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.66,0:11:49.53,japanese,,0,0,0,,フサカク様\Nそろそろ 腹減ってきたのう。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.53,0:11:54.62,japanese,,0,0,0,,そうじゃな。 ナルトちゃん\N少し休憩じゃ！ 弁当にする。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.76,0:11:58.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,(フカサク)たんと食うとけよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:03.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,(フカサク)休憩が終わったら 仙術で\N岩蛙を持ち上げてみるけんの。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:07.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,お… おっす！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:11.60,japanese,,0,0,0,,うまいじゃろ\Nかあちゃんの特製じゃけんの。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:14.43,japanese,,0,0,0,,どれも オレの大好物じゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:17.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,《意外とうまく感じた。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:22.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,やっぱり 人間から離れてる…》
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:25.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,さて 岩蛙を\N持ち上げるわけじゃが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:30.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,まずは 己の忍術チャクラだけで\N持ち上げてみんさい。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:32.79,japanese,,0,0,0,,うん！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:38.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,よし！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.03,0:12:40.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,んっ！ うぅ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:42.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,上がらねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:45.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,はい やめ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:49.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,だぁ～！ ハァ ハァ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:52.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,じゃあ 仙術チャクラを練ってみ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:54.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,おっす！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:21.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,よし！\Nもう一度 岩蛙やってみい！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:23.19,japanese,,0,0,0,,うん！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:37.73,japanese,,0,0,0,,おっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:44.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,いいぞ！ ナルトちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:48.66,japanese,,0,0,0,,うぅっ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.66,0:13:51.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,おりゃっ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:53.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,やるがな ナルト！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:58.23,japanese,,0,0,0,,《自来也ちゃんのときより\Nのみこみが早いのう この子は》
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:14:00.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,やったぁ！\Nアホッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:02.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,先人を粗末に扱うなや！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:07.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,あぁ～!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:11.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,《マヌケなのも\N自来也ちゃん以上じゃが…》
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.13,0:14:13.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,よし！ ナルトちゃん。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:15.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,倒れた全部の岩を\N元に戻すんじゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:17.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,マジか～！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:30.56,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ゼツ)八尾か…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.56,0:14:34.73,japanese,,0,0,0,,サスケは うまくやったようだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:38.23,japanese,,0,0,0,,(マダラ)九尾は ペインが持ってくる。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:45.73,japanese,,0,0,0,,(フカサク)どうやら 油を使うコントロールを\Nマスターしたようじゃな。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:47.66,japanese,,0,0,0,,次は 油を使わずに➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.66,0:14:52.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,自然エネルギーの\Nコントロールをする修業じゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:57.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,力が みなぎってくる！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.40,0:15:02.73,japanese,,0,0,0,,体内エネルギーだけを消費していく\N忍術チャクラは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:06.06,japanese,,0,0,0,,使えば使うほど 疲れていくがな。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.06,0:15:08.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,仙術チャクラは それと違って➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.96,0:15:11.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,外から エネルギーを取り入れるけん。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:15.56,japanese,,0,0,0,,疲れるどころか回復も早いんじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:17.90,japanese,,0,0,0,,そっか。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.90,0:15:23.70,japanese,,0,0,0,,《まっ 九尾のチャクラとあいまって\N異常な回復をみせとるがのう》
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:28.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,これなら\Nあれが できるかもしれねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:31.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,なんじゃ？\Nあっ！ いや その…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:34.23,japanese,,0,0,0,,なんでもねえってばよ。\Nまあ ええ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.23,0:15:36.66,japanese,,0,0,0,,それより これじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:40.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,今日はこれを ナルトちゃんに\N渡そうと思ったんじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:42.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,ん？ 何？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:44.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,本じゃ。\N本？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.03,0:15:48.83,japanese,,0,0,0,,これは 自来也ちゃんが\N最初に書いた小説じゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:52.70,japanese,,0,0,0,,ここには 自来也ちゃんの\N思いが込められておる。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:54.69,japanese,,0,0,0,,読むとええ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:03.83,japanese,,0,0,0,,『ド根性忍伝』…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.70,0:16:09.69,japanese,,0,0,0,,そろそろ観念したらどうだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:17.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,鬼ごっこも\Nそろそろ飽きてきたぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:32.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,あきらめろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:34.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,ひと言 いいか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:36.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,聞く気はねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.13,0:16:38.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,もう くたばれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.13,0:16:40.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレが あきらめるのを…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:44.76,japanese,,0,0,0,,あきらめろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:49.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,オ… オレを倒しても➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:53.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,また次の刺客が この里を襲う。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:59.60,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヘヘヘ…\Nオレたちが呪われた忍の世界に➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:03.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,生きているかぎり平穏は… ない。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.26,0:17:05.60,japanese,,0,0,0,,なら…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:08.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレが その呪いを解いてやる。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:13.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,平和ってものが もしあるなら\Nオレがそれを つかみとってやる。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.10,0:17:15.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレは あきらめない！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.96,0:17:19.86,japanese,,0,0,0,,キ… キサマは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.86,0:17:22.86,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレの名は…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:46.76,japanese,,0,0,0,,((サスケは\Nオレとの繋がりを断ち切って➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:49.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,強くなるって言ってた。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:53.76,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前なんかに\Nオレの気持は わからないって。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:59.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,エロ仙人と大蛇丸も\N昔 友達だったんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:02.76,japanese,,0,0,0,,どうして大蛇丸は 里を抜けて➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:06.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,木ノ葉崩しなんか\Nしたんだってばよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:09.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,大蛇丸が\Nおかしくなってきたのは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:11.76,japanese,,0,0,0,,両親を殺されてからだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:14.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,それからは\N禁術に とりつかれていった。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:18.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,両親に会いたかったのか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.26,0:18:23.53,japanese,,0,0,0,,それとも 両親を死に追いやった\N木ノ葉への復讐か…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.53,0:18:27.70,japanese,,0,0,0,,わしは\N親を殺されては おらんからのう。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.70,0:18:30.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,わしも お前と同じだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:33.70,japanese,,0,0,0,,アイツに 何もわかってないと\N一喝されてのう。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:36.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,そのとおり アイツのことを➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:39.69,japanese,,0,0,0,,何もわかってやれんかったの\Nかもしれん。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:45.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,だがのう…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:47.70,japanese,,0,0,0,,こんな わしでも➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.70,0:18:51.36,japanese,,0,0,0,,この忍の世に 憎しみが\Nはびこっているのは わかる。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.36,0:18:53.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,憎しみ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:57.53,japanese,,0,0,0,,その憎しみを どうにかしたいとは\N思っとるんだが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:19:01.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,どうしたらいいのか\Nわしにも まだわからん。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:02.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,だが いつかは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.96,0:19:07.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,人が 本当の意味で\N理解しあえる時代が来ると➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:09.53,japanese,,0,0,0,,わしは信じとる。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.53,0:19:12.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,なんか 難しいってばよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:14.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,答えが見つからんかったときは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.93,0:19:18.36,japanese,,0,0,0,,その答えを\Nお前に託すとしようかのう。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:22.36,japanese,,0,0,0,,オッス！ エロ仙人の頼みなら\Nしかたねえってばよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:27.06,japanese,,0,0,0,,何？ なんで笑うんだってばよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:32.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前の笑顔には救われるようじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:34.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前を弟子にして よかったわい。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:37.00,japanese,,0,0,0,,そっかぁ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:41.83,japanese,,0,0,0,,だが… わしも\Nまだ あきらめたわけじゃない。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:46.56,japanese,,0,0,0,,わしは 自分の書いた本で\Nこの世を変えるつもりじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.56,0:19:48.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,売れない その本で？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:51.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,愚か者！ そのうち バカ売れじゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:53.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,そのときになって\Nサインをねだっても➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:55.56,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前にゃ書いてやらんからのう！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:58.06,japanese,,0,0,0,,(いらねえってばよ そんなの！))
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:03.19,japanese,,0,0,0,,いらねえってばよ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:07.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,《エロ仙人には➡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.63,0:20:11.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,もっと大切なもん\Nもらってっからよ》
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.40,0:20:31.23,japanese,,0,0,0,,こう 人数が少ないと\N時間が かかるね。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.23,0:20:34.92,japanese,,0,0,0,,うるさい！ 黙って集中しろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.23,0:20:52.92,japanese,,0,0,0,,(鬼鮫)サスケ君…\Nどうやら ヘマしたようですね。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:57.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,ハハハハ… タコの足だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.80,0:20:59.76,japanese,,0,0,0,,笑うな！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.76,0:21:03.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,ハハハハッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.27,0:22:42.15,japanese,,0,0,0,,(アルザック)ここにいたのか。\N(ビスカ)アル…。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.15,0:22:45.78,japanese,,0,0,0,,(アルザック)何を読んでるんだい？\N(ビスカ)『星空の鍵』よ。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.78,0:22:48.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,ああ… ギルドでもサポートしようって➡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.46,0:22:52.65,japanese,,0,0,0,,大聖堂の書庫から\N借りてきたんだったな。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.65,0:22:54.65,japanese,,0,0,0,,(アスカ)あれ～？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.65,0:22:58.51,japanese,,0,0,0,,ん？\Nこの本 これで終わり？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.51,0:23:00.68,japanese,,0,0,0,,そうよ。\N(アルザック)どうかしたのかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.68,0:23:02.98,japanese,,0,0,0,,(アスカ)う～ん。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.50,0:00:04.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.90,0:00:09.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,How come becoming one\Nwith nature means dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.03,0:00:13.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Gamakichi, what's with the dying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.37,0:00:14.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make such weird analogies!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.80,0:00:16.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.13,0:00:22.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax. You're not actually\Ngoing to die, Naruto-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:24.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.63,0:00:27.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait 'til I'm finished...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:29.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain it stepwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.10,0:00:36.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Absorbing Nature Energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.13,0:00:38.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It means the ability to\Nsense it around you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.37,0:00:41.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,and draw it into yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.47,0:00:45.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition,\Nby becoming one with nature,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.43,0:00:48.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,you also gain full control\Nover the Nature Energy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:51.00,english,,0000,0000,0000,,entering and leaving your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.10,0:00:56.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Practically speaking,\Nin terms of your training...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.60,0:00:57.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.57,0:00:59.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit still.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.10,0:01:00.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:03.00,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It means sit still!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.77,0:01:06.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,When you cease your flow\Nof animal instincts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,and harmonize with\Nthe flow of nature,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.80,0:01:12.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,you will be able to sense\NNature Energy for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.33,0:01:15.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,So I just stay still?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.03,0:01:18.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That seems easy enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.50,0:01:21.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto, you really don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.70,0:01:29.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,For animals, not moving is\Nthe hardest thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:34.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Jumping, running, molding chakra\Nwith all my strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.50,0:01:36.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I've done those sorts of training.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:40.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But staying still? I don't quite get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.27,0:01:44.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's how you take\Nin Nature Energy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:47.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to do it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.63,0:01:50.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,This training requires time,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.57,0:01:52.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,since the degree of difficulty\Nis very high.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.40,0:01:55.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna take that long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.53,0:01:57.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take it so lightly, Naruto-boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:02:00.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Our enemy is Pain,\Nwho possesses the Rinnegan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.67,0:02:02.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of the\NSage of the Six Paths.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.57,0:02:04.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,A powerful enemy\Nwho killed Jiraiya-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:09.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,With that kind of attitude,\Nyou can't possibly win!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.93,0:02:11.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I know all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:15.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Pain is the leader of the Akatsuki,\Nwho are after Tailed Beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:17.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,They could come for me\Nat any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:19.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have much time to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:29.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not as though\Nthere isn't a better way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.63,0:02:30.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,There is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.70,0:02:32.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Then teach me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:36.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,This waterfall behind me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:40.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the secret toad oil\Nof Mount Myoboku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.33,0:02:41.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Toad oil?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:46.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Come over here and\Nput out your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:55.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:03:03.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,This toad oil has the property\Nof attracting Nature Energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:05.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It helps with the training.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.23,0:03:08.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.27,0:03:12.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever you rub this oil\Non your body,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:15.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Nature Energy can enter\Nthrough there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.87,0:03:21.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And gradually, you'll gain the ability\Nto sense Nature Energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:23.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.33,0:03:25.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I feel something\Nthrough my skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:30.00,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a tool to help grasp\Nthe concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:34.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,In time, you won't even need\Nto use the oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.33,0:03:37.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,However, there is a risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.67,0:03:45.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,When used by one who is inexperienced\Nin controlling Nature Energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:48.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,you start to turn into a frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:03:58.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:00.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:01.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna be a frog!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:06.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:08.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:10.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all about balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:15.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You're used to turning your Mental\Nand Physical Energy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:18.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,into ninjutsu chakra,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.60,0:04:20.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,so you've got a balance there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:25.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, you must add\NNature Energy into the mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.33,0:04:27.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting the perfect balance\Nis extremely difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.23,0:04:29.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Balance, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:33.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,PHYSICAL     MENTAL    NATURE\NTake in too little, and you won't\Nget Sage Jutsu chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:35.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, if you take in too much,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:39.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Nature Energy will overwhelm you\Nand turn you into a frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:45.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, if you only take in\Na little too much, it's reversible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.60,0:04:52.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But get beyond a certain amount,\Nand you'll stay as a frog,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.30,0:04:54.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,never reverting back to\Na human again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:58.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What I meant about you\Nhaving to die
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:05:01.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,is that you might stop being human.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.47,0:05:03.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you turn into a frog,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:06.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,then you progress further toward\Npermanently becoming one with nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.67,0:05:10.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And the past students\Nwho've failed in this training...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.73,0:05:14.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,are those stone statues.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:17.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.87,0:05:20.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't fret too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:24.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You have me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:29.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And this baton beats Nature Energy\Nout of one's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.77,0:05:32.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,If you start transforming into a frog,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:36.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat you thoroughly to reverse it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:40.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking truthfully,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.60,0:05:44.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,even Jiraiya-boy wasn't able\Nto completely master this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.87,0:05:49.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,When molding Sage Jutsu chakra,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.17,0:05:51.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Jiraiya-boy always acquired\Nsome frog features.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.07,0:05:54.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But he was among the skilled ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.07,0:05:58.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt that you'd hesitate\Nafter coming this far,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:00.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,but let me ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:03.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:06.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:09.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,My Ninja Way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:11.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,is the same as the Pervy Sage's!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:45.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The First Challenge\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.37,0:07:48.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally got the Six-Tails.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.33,0:07:52.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we can go on the hunt\Nfor the Nine-Tails.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:54.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.67,0:07:58.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you killed Jiraiya,\Nthe Leaf will set their eyes on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:01.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The more time passes,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:04.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,the more likely they'll set\Nsome plan in motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:07.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Take action before it becomes\Nmore difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:09.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Pain is invincible...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:13.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens,\Nwe will capture the Nine-Tails.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:16.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,There's just one more Tailed Beast left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:17.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Not two?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.17,0:08:20.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke has already captured\Nthe Eight-Tails.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:21.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:27.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Konan, make preparations immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:36.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading out to the Hidden Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.63,0:08:46.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.33,0:08:51.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, I'm going to be bruised\Nand bleeding on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:54.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Giving up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:59.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I know a much better\Ntraining method.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.77,0:09:00.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:03.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Use Shadow Clones for the training.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:06.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,They exponentially increase\Nmy progress!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:08.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.97,0:09:13.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The experience of the Shadow Clones\Nreverts back to the original.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:17.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But the reverse is also true...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:20.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,If a Shadow Clone completely\Nchanges into a frog,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:22.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,it's over for the original.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:24.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.07,0:09:27.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. But four is the limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:30.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Any more and neither the baton\Nor I can keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:31.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:45.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not playing a game\Nof whack-a-mole!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:47.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,This is training!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:48.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna last doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.07,0:09:50.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.50,0:09:53.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:57.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,My face is like this from being hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.77,0:09:59.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not turning into a frog!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:01.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:09.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought that training\Nto feel Nature Energy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:11.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,would be so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:16.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Only through perseverance shall\Ntrue strength be gained.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:18.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:21.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,If it'll make me strong like\Nthe Pervy Sage,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:23.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,anyone would endure this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:25.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,No... That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:30.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,This training is not for everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.10,0:10:36.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You could say it's only possible\Nbecause it's you and Jiraiya-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:39.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Or else I wouldn't have even\Nbrought you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:41.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:46.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you already possess\Nenormous chakra inside you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:50.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Nature Energy would just take\Nover you right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:55.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That is how intense Nature Energy is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:11:01.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, they must have the guts\Nto never give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:04.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of person who\Ncan become a Sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:09.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's do this then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:11.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! Do you want to kill yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.47,0:11:38.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.37,0:11:42.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yes!\N- {\i1}It seems he's starting
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.87,0:11:45.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,- I can see it! I can see it!\N- {\i1}to get the feel of Nature Energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:49.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,- Lord Fukasaku, I'm getting a little hungry.\N- I saw it! I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.67,0:11:50.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,- You're right.\N- I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:53.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,- Naruto-boy, time for a break.\N- I'm awesome, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:54.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:58.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:00.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,After the break,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:03.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you try to lift up\Nthe stone frogs using Sage Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.77,0:12:06.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.67,0:12:11.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, huh?\NThey're Ma's special dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:14.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all favorites of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.37,0:12:17.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That actually tasted quite good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:21.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm becoming less human, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.43,0:12:26.00,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, I want you to\Nraise the stone frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.40,0:12:30.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But first, try it using only\Nyour ninjutsu chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.07,0:12:32.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:36.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.93,0:12:42.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lift it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.23,0:12:44.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:52.00,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, mold some Sage Jutsu chakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:52.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:20.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Now try lifting\Nthe stone frog once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.43,0:13:22.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.03,0:13:36.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:44.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! Naruto-boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:53.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:58.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This lad's quicker on\N{\i1}the uptake than Jiraiya-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:13:59.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:02.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! How dare you treat your predecessor\Nwith such disrespect!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:11.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Though he's a lot denser\N{\i1}than Jiraiya-boy too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:13.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Naruto-boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:16.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Now put all the toppled stones\Nback in place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.23,0:14:18.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:30.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The Eight-Tails, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:34.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Sasuke was successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:37.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Pain will bring the Nine-Tails.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.03,0:14:45.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears you've mastered\Ntoad oil assisted control.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:49.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you need to master\Ncontrolling Nature Energy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:51.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,without using the oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.63,0:14:57.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel the power flowing into me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:15:03.00,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninjutsu chakra consumes\Nyour internal energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.03,0:15:05.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The more you use it,\Nthe more exhausted you will become.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.77,0:15:10.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,In contrast, Sage Jutsu chakra\Ndraws in external energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:12.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,so it will not tire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:15.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, you will recover and\Nheal quicker too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:18.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:21.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well... With the Nine-Tails' chakra\N{\i1}in the mix too,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:23.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he's showing a truly remarkable\N{\i1}recovery rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.47,0:15:28.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Now maybe I can do that too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.13,0:15:29.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:31.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Oh, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.77,0:15:32.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.17,0:15:36.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind then... But here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:40.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd give you\Nthis today, Naruto-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:42.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:43.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,A book.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:44.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Book?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:48.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first novel\NJiraiya-boy wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:52.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of Jiraiya-boy's mind and\Nheart are contained within it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:54.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You should read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:03.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,TALES OF A GUTSY NINJA\NTales of...a Gutsy Ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.43,0:16:09.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you give it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:17.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,This game of tag is getting boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:32.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:34.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I say one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:35.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care to listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.13,0:16:38.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Die already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:40.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:44.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,on me giving up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:50.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you bring me down,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.13,0:16:54.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,another assassin will attack\Nthe village...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:17:01.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we are cursed to\Nlive in this Ninja World,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:03.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,there will be no peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:08.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...I'll break that curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.27,0:17:13.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is such a thing as peace,\NI'll seize it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:15.00,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.53,0:17:20.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:22.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.07,0:17:26.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,TALES OF A GUTSY NINJA
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:35.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,JIRAIYA
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:47.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sasuke said he was going to\N{\i1}sever his bond with me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:48.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.57,0:17:52.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He said I could never understand\N{\i1}his feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:18:00.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You were friends with Orochimaru\N{\i1}long ago, right, Pervy Sage?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:03.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why did Orochimaru desert\N{\i1}the village
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:05.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and decide to destroy the Hidden Leaf?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.97,0:18:11.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Orochimaru changed after\N{\i1}his parents were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:15.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He became obsessed with\N{\i1}the Forbidden Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:19.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe he longed to see his parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.50,0:18:21.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or he sought revenge\N{\i1}on the Leaf Village,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:23.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who he held responsible\N{\i1}for their deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:27.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My parents weren't killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:30.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:34.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was accused of not being\N{\i1}able to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:36.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Perhaps he was right,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:39.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and I didn't understand a thing about him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:45.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:51.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even I can see there's too much hate\N{\i1}in our Ninja World.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:53.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.37,0:18:57.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I've wanted to do something\N{\i1}about this hatred,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:01.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}yet I'm not sure what must be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:03.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I have faith...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:06.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that there will come a time
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:08.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}when people can truly understand\N{\i1}one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.07,0:19:12.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It all sounds kinda complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.97,0:19:15.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if I can't find the answer,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.37,0:19:18.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}perhaps I will entrust you to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:22.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, sir! I can't turn you down,\N{\i1}can I, Pervy Sage?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.77,0:19:27.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? Why are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:30.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your smile is my salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:35.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm glad I made you my student.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.83,0:19:37.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:41.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I haven't given up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.73,0:19:46.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,PRODUCTION NOTEBOOK\N{\i1}I plan to change this world\N{\i1}with my books!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.40,0:19:49.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With those books that don't sell?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:50.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.70,0:19:52.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They'll be bestsellers before\N{\i1}you know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:54.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And when that day finally arrives,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:56.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't autograph your copies\N{\i1}even if you beg me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:57.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't need any of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.07,0:20:02.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need any of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:11.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cuz Pervy Sage... You gave me\Nsomething much more valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:31.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,With so few people,\Nit sure is taking a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:32.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.93,0:20:34.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet and focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:49.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:51.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke has blundered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.37,0:20:59.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,An octopus leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.60,0:21:00.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.73,0:22:38.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this sensation?\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.27,0:22:41.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel uncomfortable\Nbeing still at all!\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.47,0:22:45.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what it feels like to become\None with nature?\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.43,0:22:48.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not using the toad oil,\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.37,0:22:50.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can tell power is being gathered\Nfrom everywhere!\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.60,0:22:55.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel the power surging\Ninside of me!\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:22:59.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Sage Mode?!\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.33,0:23:03.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Naruto Shippuden:\N"Surpassing the Master"\N\N
